  ('HOD102', 60, 'From the mid-1930s onwards, a vast number of modern landmark designs made from plastic, were produced for the US market. What are these products? Check one option.', '{"A":"Miniature Baby Brownie Camera.","B":"Operating desk lamp (Model No. 114).","C":"Refrigerator Coldspot.","D":"All of the above."}'::jsonb, 'D', 'D. All of the above.', '[]'::jsonb, true, false, 'low', null),
