  ('HOD102', 90, 'Fill in the blank: American culture was now heavily driven by mass consumption. One of the greatest symbols of America''s new culture and its industrial ascendancy was General Motors (GM), which during the 1950s became the first corporation ever to gross .......... dollars a year .', '{"A":"nine billion","B":"ten billion","C":"five hundred million","D":"a billion"}'::jsonb, 'D', 'D. a billion', '[]'::jsonb, true, false, 'low', null),
  ('HOD102', 91, 'What are the criteria (or characteristics) of Good Design?', '{"A":"Pure forms, practical function, appropriate use of materials, restrained use of color , high-quality construction, good value for money","B":"Pure forms, practical function, appropriate use of materials, restrained use of color and emotional connections.","C":"Based on decorative details, focusing on performance, high-quality construction, good value for money","D":"Based on aesthetic value and functional use of the product, high-quality construction, good value for money"}'::jsonb, 'A', 'A. Pure forms, practical function, appropriate use of materials, restrained use of color , high-quality construction, good value for money', '[]'::jsonb, true, false, 'low', null),
