  ('HOD102', 107, 'Creative Salvage helped to revolutionize the design in much the same way that Punk changed music and fashion. Also, it was significant to the subsequent development of avant-garde design because it helped to break down traditional barriers between art, craft, and design. What is the key to Creative Salvage''s success?', '{"A":"The recycling of scrap to form stylish and functional artefacts for the home and office.","B":"The aesthetic and emotional values, use of natural materials.","C":"Prioritizing the use of natural materials scrap to form stylish and functional artefacts for the home and office.","D":"The exuberantly playful, capturing the optimism, color combinations, bold overall forms."}'::jsonb, 'A', 'A. The recycling of scrap to form stylish and functional artefacts for the home and office.', '[]'::jsonb, true, false, 'low', null),
