  ('HOD102', 130, 'In the early 1970s, which company began experimenting with cellular radio technology, and the results of those tests went on to revolutionize communication devices? In 1973 the company tested the first portable radio phone" in New York.', '{"A":"Sony","B":"Samsung","C":"Apple","D":"Motorola"}'::jsonb, 'D', 'D. Motorola', '[]'::jsonb, true, false, 'low', null),
