  ('HOD102', 180, 'What were the contributions of Bauhaus in the history of design? Check two options.', '{"A":"Bauhaus has been a force of modernization: it has transformed the style towards industrialism in design and thus deeply influenced the story of design.","B":"The Bauhaus had been a powerful modernizing force: it transformed design education and thereby profoundly influenced the story of design.","C":"Bauhaus existed for a very short time, it changed the mind of the designer , but do not deeply influence the story of the design.","D":"Bauhaus existed for a very short time but it brought about dramatic changes in the marketing of design products and thus profoundly influenced the design story."}'::jsonb, 'AB', 'A. Bauhaus has been a force of modernization: it has transformed the style towards industrialism in design and thus deeply influenced the story of design.; B. The Bauhaus had been a powerful modernizing force: it transformed design education and thereby profoundly influenced the story of design.', '[]'::jsonb, true, false, 'low', null),
